Consistent is key! Its taken me 1 year to lose 28 kilos. With the right nutrition guidance, not only has Neha helped me lose weight but she has taught me balance. Yes, for the part i eat healthy buy i have started to enjoy my week-end indulgence in moderation and not binge eat like It's my last meal ever. This to me is success! For those asking during the journey did i fall ? yes, I did but it's okay, get back up and start over do not dwell on it!
Thanks Neha for changing not just my eating habits but my mindset too..
